<COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">Yuan Chen</COREF> believed that because <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">most of <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">the developing countries</COREF></COREF> are actively promoting structural reform and adopting measures to stabilize <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> economy , <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">these countries</COREF> as a unified body have maintained a growth rate of above 6 % for 5 years running .
