<COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">Yuan Chen</COREF> also pointed out that what causes worry is that some industrial countries <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">take</COREF> labor standards , environment and human rights , etc. , as excuses to frequently adopt trade protection measures .
<COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">This</COREF> severely affects the future of world economy and trade .
